Name: [Ally] Electroboo
Desc:
All squad members' <color=#2EB6FF>Electric DMG</color> increases by <color=#2BAD00>10%</color>.
Active Skill: Charges the enemy and continuously electrocutes the target, dealing <color=#2EB6FF>Electric DMG</color> and accumulating <color=#2EB6FF>Electric Anomaly Buildup</color>.
Desc2: Small but functional, it's a great help to Proxies in the Hollows.
